# Premise

Sci-fi. (human)

4 college students, working on their own with little oversight, have been given space and funding to do scientific experiments. They are a rag-tag group, with a fair bit of inter-personal drama, but all still whip-smart scientists in their own right. (human)

They accidentally discover a mysterious means to perform experiments that seemingly break the laws of physics. The exact nature of the machine they built, and uncovering the mystery of the broken physics, is the focus of the movie. More and more hints about the machine are uncovered slowly. (human)

Ultimately, the machine gives them the ability to interact with other multiverses. (human)

# Multiverse

Most multiverse stories focus on the idea that other parallel universes have differences, and exploring the small differences and large differences these universes have. Instead, all the multiverses in this story will be exactly the same. (human)

As these multiverses start communicating with each other, these actions will start to cause the universes to diverge. Slow and minute at first, but ultimately resulting in major changes. (human)
